> tender meat, melty cheese, and lightly charred veggies? This version boasts herby,
> Italian-seasoned chicken, sautéed pepper and onion, gooey mozzarella, and a creamy
> garlic sauce. It's all stuffed inside garlic butter baguettes and served with golden
> brown potato wedges for a dinner that'll have you head over heels at first bite.